# Example ACL file — regenerated by `capagg sync_mosquitto`. Do not edit by hand.

# Aggregator consumer: read everything inbound, write outbound re-broadcasts
user capagg-consumer
topic read cap/in/#
topic write cap/out/#

# One block per registered authority — write-only to its own scoped topic
user ke-kmd
topic write cap/in/ke/kmd

user gh-gmet
topic write cap/in/gh/gmet

# Downstream subscribers (re-publication): read-only on outbound topics
user downstream-example
topic read cap/out/#
